title: Opie & Jim Norton NOV 03 2015 Tue.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton NOV 03 2015 Tue (03:11:53)


On Today's Show:

SHERROD SMALL, LOU DIAMOND PHILLIPS, TOPHER GRACE.

The Show Opens With Sherrod Small in Studio.
Rachel Dolezal says she's white Clip & Discussion.Uber driver pepper sprays drunk passenger clip & discussion. They talk about Anonymous outing members of the KKK. Jeb Bush in a hoodie into presidential candidates discussion. They talk about Jay Leno's car collection. They go through some of the items of rock memorabilia going up for auction this month. Ringo Starr in Sketchers commercial clip & talk. 

LeBron James becomes youngest player to 25000 career points discussion into other basketball talk. Oklahoma mayor apologizes after husband dresses up in KKK costume clip & discussion. An update about Quentin Tarantino's comments about police violence story. They play & discuss MSNBC host Melissa Harris-Perry objecting to a guest on her show. Yale SAE Fraternity Accused of Admitting 'White Girls Only' At Halloween Party, story discussion. 

Lou Diamond Phillips joins them and they talk about his new movie about Chilean miners ego were trapped underground five years ago, his early career, and his poker playing.

Topher Grace joins them and they talk about his new movie about Dan Rather, a jury duty experience, his former babysitter who is an actress, how he got his first acting job on That 70's Show, and his hobby website and his hobby of reediting movies
